text.tspan: Cumulative CO₂ emissions by world region
Cumulative carbon dioxide (CO₂) emissions by region from the year 1750 onwards. This measures CO₂ emissions
from fossil fuels and industry1 only – land use change is not included.
Source: Our World in Data based on the Global Carbon Project (2022)
